@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>VibeLang collects the following information when you create an account and use our platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> First name, last name, email address, and password</li>
                <li><strong>Learning Data:</strong> Courses completed, lessons progress, quiz scores, vocabulary progress, and XP earned</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device type, and access timestamps</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use the collected information for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>To provide and maintain our language learning platform</li>
                <li>To track your learning progress and personalize your experience</li>
                <li>To display your achievements on leaderboards and progress dashboards</li>
                <li>To improve our services and develop new features</li>
                <li>To send notifications about your learning activity (if opted in)</li>
                <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">3. Data Security</h2>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Encryption of sensitive data in transit and at rest</li>
                <li>Secure password hashing using ASP.NET Identity</li>
                <li>Regular security updates and vulnerability assessments</li>
                <li>Access controls and authentication mechanisms</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">4. Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We only share your data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>With our administrators and moderators to manage the platform</li>
                <li>When required by law or government authorities</li>
                <li>To protect our legal rights or prevent fraud</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">5. Your Learning Profile Visibility</h2>
            <p>Your learning progress and achievements may be visible to other users through leaderboards and public profiles, 
            depending on your privacy settings. You can modify these settings in your account preferences.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">6. Data Retention</h2>
            <p>We retain your personal data for as long as your account is active. Upon account deletion, your data will be 
            removed from our active systems within 30 days, except where retention is required by law.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>You have the right to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your personal data</li>
                <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
                <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
                <li>Opt-out of non-essential communications</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">8. Cookie Policy</h2>
            <p>VibeLang uses cookies to enhance user experience, maintain session information, and analyze usage patterns. 
            You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p>Our platform may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these 
            third-party sites. Please review their privacy policies before providing any personal information.</p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4 mb-3">10. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us at:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@vibelang.com<br>
                <strong>Support:</strong> support@vibelang.com
            </p>

            <hr class="my-4">
            <p class="text-muted small">
                <strong>Last Updated:</strong> May 3, 2026<br>
                This privacy policy may be updated periodically. We will notify users of any significant changes via email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
